item.title: How do i make new items appear?
item.dc:creator: @mojobo1 mojobo1
item.description:
@mojobo1 wrote:

yo, im new myself so im not exactly sure, i can make random items appear, but i dont know how to make the items i want appear. so far i figured out this: type “::pickup #### ##” in the first 4 #'s type 4 random numbers… like… 2354 and in the second #'s type in how many of the items you want… if its a noted item, or is stakable it makes however many items you tell it, if its not though it just makes one. for an example… “::pickup 1234 10” exactly how i did it, no spaces before the :: and the spaces where i put them.

to find out commands yourself… click “help” then “command list” its on the moparscape window where you can log in. it has all the commands and stuff there.

(its off topic, but type “::bank” to use a bank from ANYWHERE)

hope it helps!
